g.text: Johnny is the self-taught computer science student. He is studying how to do a machine, however, some of the material the he found online is too complex. Therefore, he wasted more time to read and comprehend those he do not understand. He wish that they is a step-to-step material to help him understand the knowledge related to his research project.MotivationsSave time and be more productiveGather the information in the correct levelGoalsGetting the material in the correct difficulty and easy to follow.Pain pointsDifficulty of the material is not rightCannot understand the material onlineGetting the information might be long because of is not that right, he might lose time because of thatNameJonny SinsAge20Rolestudent“As a student, I am learning about the programming, but the material found is too hard”
